show.description: Panatha sambaricha mattum podhadhu, adha eppadi namakka payanpadura vagaiyula semikkanum nu therijikkanum. Adhu mattum illa, Oru thalai murai sambaricha panatha correct ah save panna, adutha rendu thalai murai kashta pada theva illa nu indha audio book la namma guest pesi irukaaru. Avaru yaaru, Money management pathi ennalam pesi irukaaru nu indha audio book la kettu therinjikonga.
